This application uses third-party components and services:

1. The Movie Database (TMDB) API
   - Used for movie data, posters, and metadata
   - This product uses the TMDB API but is not endorsed or certified by TMDB
   - TMDB terms: https://www.themoviedb.org/documentation/api/terms-of-use

2. Firebase Services (Google)
   - Firebase Authentication for user login
   - Firestore for cloud data storage
   - Terms: https://firebase.google.com/terms

3. Android Jetpack Libraries (Google)
   - Jetpack Compose
   - ViewModel
   - Room
   - WorkManager
   - Licensed under Apache License 2.0

4. Third-Party Libraries:
   - Retrofit (Square) - Apache License 2.0
   - Coil (Image loading) - Apache License 2.0
   - Kotlin Coroutines - Apache License 2.0

5. Icons & Assets:
   - App icons and UI illustrations are original or licensed for use
   - Movie posters and images are sourced from TMDB API
   - Material Design Icons (Google) - Apache License 2.0

